ed="T" n="0815b22"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0815b22"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000013215"><placeName>越州</placeName><placeName>焦山</placeName><placeName>大曆寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A009615">神邕</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0815b23"/><persName key="A009615">釋神邕</persName>，字<persName key="A009615">道恭</persName>，姓<name>蔡</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000000103">東晉</placeName>太尉<persName key="A011856">謨</persName>──即度江<lb
ed="T" n="0815b24"/>祖──十五代孫也。因官居于<placeName key="PL000000013376">暨陽</placeName>，<persName key="A009615">邕</persName>生于是<lb
ed="T" n="0815b25"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000013376">邑</ref>。母<persName key="A019418">宣<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>始娠之際，率多徵異。襁褓中聞<lb
ed="T" n="0815b26"/>唱經聲，必有凝神側聽之貌。丱角聰<anchor xml:id="beg0815004"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>䎸</sic><corr>晤</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0815004"/>過<lb
ed="T" n="0815b27"/>人。<date key="j19844351984789" from-iso="+0721-02-05" to-iso="+0722-01-25">年十二</date>辭親學道<ptr target="#n2239"/>，請業於<placeName key="PL000000013292">法華寺</placeName><persName key="A010840">俊<roleName>師</roleName></persName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0815b28"/>每覽<name>孔</name><name>釋</name>二典，一讀能誦。同輩者罕不欣<lb
ed="T" n="0815b29"/>慕。<date from-iso="+0738-01-29" key="j19906371991020" to-iso="+0739-02-16"><name>開元</name>二十六年</date>，勅度隸<placeName key="PL000000013365"><placeName>諸暨</placeName><placeName>香嚴寺</placeName></placeName>名藉。<pb ed="T" n="0815c" xml:id="T50.2061.0815c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0815c01"/>依<placeName key="PL000000013292">法華寺</placeName><persName key="A010815">玄儼<roleName>師</roleName></persName>，通《四分律鈔》<ptr target="#n1290"/>。<persName key="A010815">儼</persName>識其志<lb
ed="T" n="0815c02"/>氣，謂人曰：「此<ref type="person" target="#A009615">子</ref>數年後，卒為學者之司南<lb
ed="T" n="0815c03"/>矣。爾其勉之！」<persName key="A010815">儼</persName>新出《輔篇律記》<ptr target="#n28"/>，<persName key="A009615">邕</persName>抉其膏<lb
ed="T" n="0815c04"/>腴，窮彼衢術，一宗學者少能與其聯<anchor xml:id="beg0815sgsz11"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>鏕</sic><corr>鑣</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0815sgsz11"/>方<lb
ed="T" n="0815c05"/>軌<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1085"/>焉。性非局促，又從<placeName key="PL000000013557">左溪</placeName><persName key="A009605">玄朗</persName>師習天台<lb
ed="T" n="0815c06"/>止觀、禪門<ptr target="#n2217"/>、《法華玄疏》<ptr target="#n1171"/>、《梵網經》<ptr target="#n2214"/>等，四教<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1089"/>三觀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g393"/>等<lb
ed="T" n="0815c07"/>義，祕<anchor xml:id="beg0815005"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>犍</sic><corr>鍵</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0815005"/>載<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1103"/>啟，觀性知空，爰至五夏，果精<lb
ed="T" n="0815c08"/>敷演，<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName><placeName key="PL000000013239">會</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0815sgsz13"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>問</sic><corr>閒</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0815sgsz13"/>學者從之。<date notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14" key="j19921141997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15"><name>天寶</name>中</date><ref type="place" target="#PL000000013376">本邑</ref><persName key="A011862">郭密之</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0815c09"/>請居<placeName key="PL000000058223">法樂寺</placeName>西坊，恢拓佛舍，層閣摩霄，半<lb
ed="T" n="0815c10"/>澄江影，廊宇完備。後乃遊問<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>，居<placeName key="PL000000042147">安國<lb
ed="T" n="0815c11"/>寺</placeName>，公卿藉其風宇，迫慕者結轍而至。方欲<lb
ed="T" n="0815c12"/>大闡禪律，倏遇<persName key="A008454">祿山</persName>兵亂<ptr target="#n382"/>，東歸<placeName key="PL000000008364">江湖</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1100"/>，經歷<lb
ed="T" n="0815c13"/><placeName key="PL000000027119">襄陽</placeName>，御史中丞<persName key="A023380">庾<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>光先</sic><corr>準</corr></choice></persName>出鎮<placeName key="PL000000027770">荊南</placeName><ptr target="#n2234"/>，邀留數月。<lb
ed="T" n="0815c14"/>時給事中<persName key="A011866">竇紹</persName>、中書舍人<persName key="A011868">苑咸</persName>，鑽仰彌高<ptr target="#n842"/>，俱<lb
ed="T" n="0815c15"/>受心要。著作郎<persName key="A011873">韋子春</persName>──<placeName key="PL000000000106">有唐</placeName>之外臣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1105"/>也，剛氣<lb
ed="T" n="0815c16"/>而贍學──與之詶抗。<persName key="A011873">子春</persName>折角<ptr type="glossary" target="#g298"/>，滿座驚服。<persName key="A011868">苑<roleName>舍<lb
ed="T" n="0815c17"/>人</roleName></persName>歎曰：「闍梨可謂塵外摩尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1106"/>，論中師子！」時人<lb
ed="T" n="0815c18"/>以為能言矣。旋居故鄉<placeName key="PL000000013292">法華寺</placeName>，殿中侍御<lb
ed="T" n="0815c19"/>史<persName key="A010971">皇甫曾</persName>、大理評事<persName key="A011876">張河</persName><ptr target="#n2236"/>、金吾衛長史<persName key="A011070">嚴維</persName>、兵<lb
ed="T" n="0815c20"/>曹<persName key="A011140">呂渭</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013376">諸暨</placeName>長<persName key="A010326">丘丹</persName>、校書<persName key="A011877">陳允初</persName>賦詩往復<ptr target="#n2235"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0815c21"/><persName key="A011881">盧士式</persName>為之序，引以繼<persName key="A002205">支</persName>、<persName key="A002695">許</persName>之遊，為<ref type="place" target="#PL000000013376">邑</ref>中<lb
ed="T" n="0815c22"/>故事。<persName key="A009615">邕</persName>修念之外，時綴文句，有集十卷，<persName key="A010971">皇<lb
ed="T" n="0815c23"/>甫曾</persName>為序。自<date notBefore-iso="+0756-08-16" key="j19974112005747" notAfter-iso="+0779-06-13"><name>至德</name>迄<name>大曆</name>中</date>，頻受請登壇<lb
ed="T" n="0815c24"/>度戒，起<placeName key="PL000000011045">丹陽</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0815006"/>洎<anchor xml:id="end0815006"/>乎<placeName key="PL000000013517">金華</placeName>，其間<name>釋</name>子皆命為<lb
ed="T" n="0815c25"/>親教師<ptr type="glossary" target="#g128"/>也。又以<ref type="place" target="#PL000000013376">縣</ref>南路通<placeName key="PL000000013661">衢</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013518">婺</placeName>，其中百餘<lb
ed="T" n="0815c26"/>里殊無伽藍，<name>釋</name>侶往來宴息無所。<persName key="A009615">邕</persName>願布<lb
ed="T" n="0815c27"/>法橋，接憩行旅，遂於<placeName key="PL000000013203">焦山</placeName>可以為<name>梵</name>場<lb
ed="T" n="0815c28"/>也。得<ref type="place" target="#PL000000013376">邑</ref>人騎都尉<persName key="A011882">陳紹欽</persName>等率群信搆淨<lb
ed="T" n="0815c29"/>剎，一紀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g122"/>方乃集事焉。前吏部侍郎<persName key="A008847">徐浩</persName>出佐<pb ed="T" n="0816a" xml:id="T50.2061.0816a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0816a01"/><placeName key="PL000000012470">明州</placeName>，以邦國聚落，乃白廉使<persName key="A011908">皇甫溫</persName>奏賜<lb
ed="T" n="0816a02"/>額曰<placeName key="PL000000013215">大曆</placeName>焉。先是，<placeName key="PL000000023253">中岳</placeName>道士<persName key="A011909">吳筠</persName>造邪論<lb
ed="T" n="0816a03"/>數篇<ptr target="#n2237"/>，斥毀<name>釋</name>教，昏蒙者惑之。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000011308">本道</ref>觀察使<lb
ed="T" n="0816a04"/><persName key="A010312">陳少遊</persName>請<persName key="A009615">邕</persName>決<name>釋</name>、<name>老</name>二教孰為至道，乃襲<lb
ed="T" n="0816a05"/><persName key="A002799">世尊</persName>之攝邪見，復<persName key="A002876">寶琳</persName>之破魔文<ptr target="#n2215"/>，爰據城塹，<lb
ed="T" n="0816a06"/>以正制狂。旗鼓纔臨，<persName key="A011909">吳筠</persName>覆轍。遂著《破倒<lb
ed="T" n="0816a07"/>翻迷論》三卷，東方佛法再興，實<persName key="A009615">邕</persName>之力歟。末<lb
ed="T" n="0816a08"/>遊<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>，又纂地誌兩卷<ptr target="#n2218"/>，並附於新論矣。<persName key="A009615">邕</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0816a09"/>廞頤豐角<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1093"/>，風韻朗拔，前後廉問<ptr type="glossary" target="#g979"/>皆延置別榻，<lb
ed="T" n="0816a10"/>請為僧統<ptr target="#n2238"/>，以加崇揖之禮。<date key="j20092252009225" when-iso="+0788-12-20"><name>貞元</name>四年戊辰歲<lb
ed="T" n="0816a11"/>十一月十四日</date>，遇疾，遺教門人，趺坐端相而<lb
ed="T" n="0816a12"/>歸寂于<placeName key="PL000000013215">大曆</placeName>法堂焉。以<date key="j20092542009254" when-iso="+0789-01-18">十二月十四日</date>奉<lb
ed="T" n="0816a13"/>靈儀於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000013215">寺</ref>北原，遵僧制也。報齡七十九，法<lb
ed="T" n="0816a14"/>歲五十。<date from-iso="+0789-11-26" key="j20095662009594" to-iso="+0789-12-24">明年冬十一月</date>方建塔矣。祕書省校<lb
ed="T" n="0816a15"/>書郎<persName key="A011911">陸淮</persName><ptr target="#n2240"/>為其銘，上首弟子<persName key="A011912">智昂</persName>、<persName key="A011069">靈澈</persName>、<persName key="A011913">進明</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0816a16"/><persName key="A011914">慧照</persName>等咸露鋒頴，禪律互傳。至<date from-iso="+0795-01-30" key="j20114572011840" to-iso="+0796-02-17">十一年</date>，戶<lb
ed="T" n="0816a17"/>部員外郎<ptr type="glossary" target="#g381"/><persName key="A011915">丘上卿</persName>為碑紀德焉。</p>
